## EDGE CASES & EXCEPTIONS

### Case 1: User Wants Detection Only
Run Phases 1-2 only. Ask: "Would you like me to humanize this?"

### Case 2: Text is Already Human
Report: "Good news! This shows strong human writing signals. AI probability: [Low]%"
